<div id="pf55" class="pf w14 hd" data-page-no="55"><div class="pc pc55 w14 hd"><img class="bi x0 y0 w15 he" alt="" src="bg55.png"/><div class="t m689 xd5 h19 yad2 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 11 September 7-13 </div><div class="t m53a x4 h36 yad3 ff1 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">E </div><div class="t m2f x3e h36 yad3 ff1 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m60a x37 h44 yad3 ff2 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ith2 0</div><div class="t m7ed x90 h44 yad3 ff2 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m7ee x58 h44 yad3 ff2 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">02E[lear </div><div class="t m4f5 x24 h19 y3d1 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Is any sick among you? let him call </div><div class="t m717 x52 h19 y73f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the elders of the church; and let </div><div class="t m401 x52 h19 y740 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them pray over him, anointing him </div><div class="t m450 x52 h19 y741 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with oil in the name of the Lord: and </div><div class="t m2d3 x52 h19 yad4 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the prayer of faith shall save the sick, </div><div class="t m1f5 x52 h19 yad5 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the Lord shall raise him up; and if </div><div class="t m246 x52 h19 yad6 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he have committed sins, they shall be </div><div class="t m2d8 x52 h19 ya16 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forgiven him. Confess your faults one </div><div class="t m7ef x52 h19 yad7 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to another, and pray one for another, </div><div class="t mc3 x52 h19 ya18 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that ye may be healed. The effectual </div><div class="t m7f0 x52 h19 ya19 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fervent prayer of a righteous man </div><div class="t m7f1 x52 h19 ya1a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">availeth much&quot; (James 5:14-16). </div><div class="t m565 xd9 h17 yad8 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">One of Job&apos;s major problems was </div><div class="t m6cb x52 h17 yad9 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">physical illness. The record says, </div><div class="t m381 x52 h17 ya1e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Satan left the Lord&apos;s presence and </div><div class="t m54b x52 h17 y33 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">made sores break out all over Job&apos;s </div><div class="t m7f2 x52 h17 ya1f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">body&quot; (Job 2:7, TEV). Job refers to his </div><div class="t m7f3 x52 h17 ya20 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">physical suffering in chapter 7, verses </div><div class="t m537 x52 h17 yada ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3 through 5: </div><div class="t m7f4 xd9 h17 ya21 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Month after month I have nothing </div><div class="t m7f5 xcf h17 ya22 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to live for; </div><div class="t m47d xd6 h17 yadb ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">night after night brings me grief. </div><div class="t m736 xd9 h17 ya23 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When I lie down to sleep, the hours </div><div class="t m3aa xc8 h17 yadc ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">drag; </div><div class="t m7f6 xd6 h17 yadd ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I toss all night and long for dawn. </div><div class="t m7f7 xd9 h17 ya26 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">My body is full of worms; </div><div class="t m65a xd6 h17 ya27 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it is covered with scabs; </div><div class="t m39b xd6 h17 yade ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pus runs out of my sores&quot; (TEV). </div><div class="t m7f8 x8e h17 y3ec ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">And again, &apos; At night my bones all </div><div class="t m48c x8f h17 y3d2 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ache; the pain that gnaws me never </div><div class="t mf9 x8f h17 yadf ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stops&quot; (Job 30:17, TEV). </div><div class="t m490 x8e h17 y94f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job was one of millions who have </div><div class="t m590 x90 h17 y3d4 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">suffered physical pain. The alleviation </div><div class="t m27b x8f h17 y3d5 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of human suffering has become a </div><div class="t m26f x8f h17 y3d6 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gigantic enterprise. Yet suffering </div><div class="t m7f9 x8f h17 yae0 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">continues to make life hard for the </div><div class="t m287 x90 h17 y3d7 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">human race. </div><div class="t m571 x8e h17 yae1 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The ministry of Jesus brought hope </div><div class="t m7fa x90 h17 yae2 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the sufferer. One of His main </div><div class="t m7fb x8f h17 y3da ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">activities was the healing of the sick. </div><div class="t m7fc x8f h17 yae3 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Whithersoever he entered, into </div><div class="t m7fd x90 h17 yae4 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">villages, or cities, or country, they laid </div><div class="t m3ab x90 h17 y745 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the sick in the streets, and besought </div><div class="t m6b3 x90 h17 y746 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">him that they might touch if it were but </div><div class="t m7fe x90 h17 yae5 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the border of his garment: and as </div><div class="t m264 x90 h17 yae6 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">many as touched him were made </div><div class="t m475 x90 h17 y951 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whole&quot; (Mark 6:56). </div><div class="t m7ff x58 h17 y748 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The apostles of Jesus received </div><div class="t m800 x90 h17 yae7 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power to continue this healing </div><div class="t m801 x90 h17 y3f5 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ministry, and it became an important </div><div class="t m802 x90 h17 y749 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">function of the early church. It is listed </div><div class="t m803 x90 h17 y3f7 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as one of the gifts of the Spirit. </div><div class="t m804 x58 h17 y74a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In our present day, much is said </div><div class="t m7ac x90 h17 yae8 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">about &quot;faith healing.&quot; Popular books </div><div class="t m805 x90 h17 yae9 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by faith healers recount story after </div><div class="t m806 x90 h17 yaea ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">story of successful healings. Other </div><div class="t m804 x90 h17 y3fb ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">observersjpoint to a much larger </div><div class="t m477 x90 h17 yaeb ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">number of attempted but </div><div class="t m289 x90 h17 yaec ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unsuccessful &quot;cures.&quot; </div><div class="t m791 x58 h17 y74d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The purpose of this lesson is to </div><div class="t m807 x90 h17 y3fe ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">survey the concept of divine </div><div class="t m808 x90 h17 yaed ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">healing—or faith healing as it is often </div><div class="t m4b6 x90 h17 yaee ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">called—and to endeavor to come to an </div><div class="t m809 x90 h17 yaef ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">understanding of this subject that will </div><div class="t m422 x90 h17 yaf0 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be useful to Christians in our day. </div><div class="t m65 x90 h19 y85 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m63 x90 h19 yaf1 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m5a8 x91 h19 y404 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Investment in Man </div><div class="t m80a x91 h19 y95a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gen. 1:26; 2:7) </div><div class="t m65 x90 h19 yaf2 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m401 x91 h19 yaf3 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Desire to Heal </div><div class="t m1ea x91 h19 y95b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 12:28) </div><div class="t m67 x90 h19 yaf4 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m5f7 x91 h19 y755 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Faith and Healing </div><div class="t m80b x91 h19 y756 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(James 5:15) </div><div class="t m69 x90 h19 yaf5 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m83 x91 h19 yaf6 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Love and Healing </div><div class="t m120 x91 h19 y95d ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 20:30-34) </div><div class="t m6b x90 h19 yaf7 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m7cd x91 h19 yaf8 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Goodness and Healing </div><div class="t m80b x91 h19 yaf9 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(James 5:16) </div><div class="t m6d x90 h19 y55a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t me4 x91 h19 yafa ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Gift of the Spirit </div><div class="t m7df x91 h19 yafb ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 12:4, 8, 9) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
